import React from 'react'
import {
    SidebarContainer,
    Icon,
    CloseIcon,
    SidebarWrapper,
    SidebarMenu,
    SidebarLink
} from "./SidebarElements"

const Sidebar = ({isOpen, toggle}) => {
    return (
        <>
            <SidebarContainer isOpen={isOpen} onClick={toggle}>
                <Icon onClick={toggle}>
                    <CloseIcon />
                </Icon>
                <SidebarWrapper>
                    <SidebarMenu>
                        <SidebarLink to="about">About Me</SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink to="projects">CS Projects</SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink to="extracurriculars">Extracurriculars</SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink to="contact">Contact Me</SidebarLink>
                    </SidebarMenu>
                </SidebarWrapper>
            </SidebarContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
